Known homozygous dihydropyrimidine dehydrogenase (DPD) deficiency;
Gilbert’s syndrome or homozygosity for UGT1A1∗28 allele;
Pregnancy or breastfeeding at time of enrollment or subsequent randomizations;
Medical conditions rendering the participant incapable of tolerating approximately six months of combination chemotherapy or interfering with safe conduct of the study.

